* Short-billed gull, &quot;Larus brachyrhynchus&quot;

The name can also refer to:
* Percival Mew Gull, 1930s British racing aircraft</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q26427" start="58" end="69" title="Common gull" label="Common gull"/>
